<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />I said, "Yahweh, have mercy on me!</para>

<para style="q1">Heal me, for I have sinned against you."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />My enemies speak evil against me, saying,</para>

<para style="q1">'When will he die and his name perish?'</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />If my enemy comes to see me, he says worthless things;</para>

<para style="q1">his heart gathers up my disaster for itself;</para>

<para style="q1">when he goes away from me, he tells others about it.</para>
